uk.knightz.knightzapi.reflect

Class ReflectionOptions<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.knightz.knightzapi.reflect.ReflectionOptions<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of Object

    public class ReflectionOptions<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Wrapper class defining a number of Reflexive operation options that are used in any automatic generation classes such as CollectionToMenuAdapter and SuperFancyMessageFactory The methodsToIgnore is also used when collecting a Set of Getters in Reflection.getUserFriendlyPublicGetters(Class, ReflectionOptions)
